All configurable values are in include/config.h:
SettingDefaultDescriptionWIFI_TIMEOUT20000WiFi connection timeout (ms)SENSOR_READ_INTERVAL2000Sensor reading frequency (ms)SLEEP_TIMEOUT120000Inactivity before sleep (ms)HEART_RATE_MIN50Minimum healthy heart rateHEART_RATE_MAX120Maximum healthy heart rateBATTERY_LOW_THRESHOLD20Low battery warning (%)

üîß Troubleshooting
NFC Not Working

Check I2C connections (SDA=21, SCL=22)
Verify PN532 is in I2C mode (check DIP switches)
Test with I2C scanner sketch

WiFi Connection Fails

Verify SSID and password in config.h
Check 2.4GHz WiFi (ESP32 doesn't support 5GHz)
Increase WIFI_TIMEOUT if network is slow

Sensors Not Reading

Check all I2C devices are on same bus
Verify power supply (3.3V for sensors)
Use I2C scanner to detect addresses

Display Blank

Verify OLED address (default 0x3C)
Check contrast settings
Ensure proper power connection


